                            Systems at the Indonesian Open University. I'm
                            interested in UI/UX Design and FullStack. I am
                            proficient in using Figma software. Apart from that,
                            I am also proficient with illustrator tools like
                            Adobe Illustrator. I also have communication, design
                            thinking and problem solving skills. I'm currently
                            studying FullStack Developer at DumbWays Indonesia
                        </p>
                        </p>
                        <div class="py-2 text-lg-start text-center">
                            <a
                                href="/comtact-me"
                                class="btn btn-dark py-1 px-3 rounded-pill text-white text-decoration-none"
                                >Contact</a
                            >
                            <a
                                href="../assets/doc/CV Hilal Akbar.pdf"
                                class="text-dark text-decoration-none ms-3"
                                >Download CV
                                <img
                                    src="../assets/img/arrow_download_icon.png"
                                    alt=""
                                    height="20"
                            /></a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="media text-lg-start text-center">
                            <span class="fa-stack">
                                <i
                                    class="fa-solid fa-circle fa-stack-2x text-center"
                                ></i>
                                <a
                                    href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/hilal-akbar/"
                                    target="_blank"
                                >
                                    <i
                                        class="fa-brands fa-linkedin-in fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"
                                    ></i>
                                </a>
                            </span>
                            <span class="fa-stack">
                                <i class="fa-solid fa-circle fa-stack-2x"></i>
                                <a
                                    href="https://github.com/akbr-hilal"
                                    target="_blank"
                                >
                                    <i
                                        class="fa-brands fa-github fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"
                                    ></i>
                                </a>
                            </span>
                            <span class="fa-stack">
                                <i class="fa-solid fa-circle fa-stack-2x"></i>
                                <a
                                    href="https://www.facebook.com/akbrhilal/"
                                    target="_blank"
                                >
                                    <i
                                        class="fa-brands fa-facebook-f fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"
                                    ></i>
                                </a>
                            </span>
                            <span class="fa-stack">
                                <i class="fa-solid fa-circle fa-stack-2x"></i>
                                <a
                                    href="https://www.instagram.com/akbr_hilal/"
                                    target="_blank"
                                >
                                    <i
                                        class="fa-brands fa-instagram fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"
                                    ></i>
                                </a>
                            </span>
